entries.arrived_at_delivery: pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < pcontrast1 Designated delivery point reached. pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < pcontrast1 Designated pickup point reached. pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: Enemy craft detected on attack vector.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: The docking is complete, I'll take that beacon.  I'm going to send the next set of orders over a secure channel.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: The hookup is good, we are sending over a package with a homing beacon the Black Sun attached. This package is a dud, they were trying to track some sensor arrays.  Take it to my partner a couple clicks off, he'll have more instructions there.
entries.found_loc_d: pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < pcontrast1 Contact point for deliver ship has been received. pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc_p: pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < pcontrast1 Contact point for contact ship has been received. pcontrast3 >
entries.hello_d: pcontrast3 Transmission: < pcontrast1 Standing by to receive cargo. pcontrast3 >
entries.hello_p: pcontrast3 Transmission: < pcontrast1 Hello there, we have the cargo you are expecting. Move into position for docking procedure. pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_dock1_d: Dock with this target to pick up a transmission beacon
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with this target to deliver the transmission beacon
entries.quest_location_d: A meeting point in the Dantooine System
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: Meet the Interdiction craft to pick up a Black Sun spy beacon
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Meet antother interdiction craft that will take the beacon to confuse the Black Sun operatives
entries.split_quest_alert: pcontrast3 Interdiction Craft: < pcontrast1 [SECURE] A freighter is coming in on this point. They will be throwing out some interference to shield your presence.  Travel with them to get into position, CorSec command will update you when they have more information [SECURE] pcontrast3 >
entries.title: Dantooine System: Rendezvous with a CorSec contact
